* Lakeflow\nConnect
** Managed Connectors
***_ Salesforce, ServiceNow, SharePoint
***_ SQL Server, Google Analytics, Workday
***_ Handles auth & rate limiting
***_ Serverless compute
** Standard Connectors
***_ Cloud storage (S3, ADLS, GCS)
***_ Kafka, Pub/Sub, Pulsar
***_ Uses Auto Loader under the hood
** Scheduling
***_ Scheduled (hourly/daily/weekly)
***_ On-demand trigger
** Output
***_ Writes to streaming tables
***_ Governed by Unity Catalog
@endmindmap
